			<h2 class='text-[#232656] font-bold'>Why we exist</h2>
			<p class='text-[#232656] text-2xl'>
				With the Ranks was founded by members of the Bernie 2020 technology team. Together, we supported one of the largest organizing operations in history, helping funnel thousands of volunteers to take real on-the-ground action and raise millions of dollars from small donors.
			</p>
			<p class='text-[#232656] text-2xl'>
				On the campaign we built and optimized <a href="https://berniesanders.com" target="_blank">berniesanders.com</a> into a powerhouse fundraising and organizing vessel, built an in-house relational organizing app called <a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2020-election/bernie-sanders-2020-campaign-unveils-app-increase-its-voter-database-n999206" target="_blank">BERN</a> that provided a critical organizing lifeline when the COVID-19 pandemic hit, and supported an operation of hundreds of staff and thousands of volunteers with a team of only 7.
			</p>
			<p class='text-[#232656] text-2xl'>
				Along the way we learned a thing or two about the intersection of organizing, data, media and technology - most importantly that building a technology operation is hard, especially under the intense time and monetary constraints most campaigns and organizations find themselves.
			</p>
			<p class='text-[#232656] text-2xl'>
				We started With the Ranks to create a better place to build organizing tech - and to make sure organizations of all sizes and budgets can have access to it. <strong>After all, change can only happen from the bottom up.</strong>
			</p>
