		<div id='our-cooperative'>
			<h2 class='text-[#232656] font-bold' style='line-break: anywhere;'>
				How we run our cooperative.
			</h2>
			<p class='text-[#232656] text-2xl'>
				We believe in the power of cooperatives to fundamentally change the way we live and work, and With the Ranks was built to provide a more sustainable model for building organizing tech. Here are a few core beliefs we have about how our business should operate:
			</p>
			<h3 class='text-[#232656] font-bold text-3xl' style='line-break: anywhere;'>
				Every worker should have ownership in the business
			</h3>
			<p class='text-[#232656] text-2xl'>
				From democratic decision-making to co-ownership of the business, With the Ranks is owned and run by its workers. That means that everyone involved cares deeply about our work and shares equally in our successes and failures. And when the business does well, we share equally in those profits.
			</p>
			<h3 class='text-[#232656] font-bold text-3xl' style='line-break: anywhere;'>
				Our pay and benefits should be fair and competitive with industry standards
			</h3>
			<p class='text-[#232656] text-2xl'>
				We can't expect talented people to work on big problems unless we support them adequately. We aim to pay our workers competitive wages and offer generous benefits, and everyone at With the Ranks makes the same salary.
			</p>
			<p class='text-[#232656] text-2xl'>
				We're slowly building out our benefits offerings, most recently adding dental through our friends at the <a href="https://www.usworker.coop" target="_blank">United States Federation of Worker Cooperatives</a>.
			</p>
			<h3 class='text-[#232656] font-bold text-3xl' style='line-break: anywhere;'>
				Tech alone won't save us
			</h3>
			<p class='text-[#232656] text-2xl'>
				Technology cannot solve the world's problems alone, but it can help scale organizing efforts. We aim to support good organizations of all sizes, regardless of their budgets, and move as many people to action as possible.
			</p>
			<a href='/public/assets/operating-agreement.pdf' target="_blank"><p>Want to know more? Read our full operating agreement here ⤳</p></a>
		</div>
